column5: 244 days, 14 hours and 22 minutes until the NARDA GANG leaves for Birch Dale Lodge.
170 days until I will be on the water at Anderson's Manitou Falls, English River, Ear Falls.
152 brutal days to wait A glorious week of fishing on Wabakimi awaits.
219 looooong days until we go to Abamasagi for the first time!
139 days Eddie North Beteau lake
155 days to Ghost River
141 LONG days till we hit up Easey Lake using Hawk Air.. I'm obviuosly much more excited then I should be with 5 months wait ahead of me..
151 days to Lake Vermilion, MN 225 days to the first Lac Seul trip 256 days to the last Lac Seul trip So much tackle. So little time to organize and re-organize.
176 Days until my first fly-in with Air Tamarac to Lac Hebert.
204 days & counting down to our trip back to Lac Seul!

Now that 2012 now lies before us, it seems like the time to start a 2012 countdown thread. For our group, heading to Goose Bay Camp in the shores of the NW end of Lac Seul, we have 163 days to go before we hit the Lac in search of the tasty walleye.How about your group?
Not including today (as it would just make it a longer personal countdown...) we have 136 days till we get to Donnelly's Minnitaki Lodge.
134 until we pull out for opening week on Wine Lake
204 Days Garden Island Lodge..........I can't wait!Here's what we have waiting for us!!!FC
191 days unless I hit the lottery.
211 days till we pull out and head to Lac Seul. Hope everyone has a great year!!!
163 days until fishing on Nagagami Lake with Expeditions North.
156 days until the first trip (unless Lovetofish wins the lottery and takes me earlier). Keep buying those tickets!!
148 days to Manitou Falls on the English River!
170 days until we will be fishing the NW & SW sections of Lac Seul.
